description: Forest Department - Order to declare the Delgoda Forest in Delgoda, Kalawana D/S Division and the Thibbotukanda Forest in Karandana (Part), Eheliyagoda D/S Division and the Muwagankanda Forest in Elapatha and Ratnapura D/S Division, Ratnapura District as Conservation Forests and the Koppakanda Forest in Kolonna D/S Division, Ratnapura District and the Nelumpath wewa Forest in Ambanpola D/S Division, Kurunegala District as Reserved Forests
